Text: This is a fascinating movie about one of the top 2 or 3 political figures of the last 40 years, whether you like him or whether you think he's Darth Vader.

Thanks for sharing this, and for doing so in a modern format (e.g. x264 or MP4 in an .mp4 or .mkv container) instead of the ridiculously antiquated, easily corruptible, and lower quality XviD codec and .avi container.
